{"tid":2155222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"化驗所送漏樣本致男警相隔5日終列確診      張竹君︰比較例外","createTime":"2020-08-13T15:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T15:59:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8fe23d5b4554efcfa54823903debf9998f8990","tid":2155222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Tu_1clYOkNGrnBQf3ZQJJw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200813a180150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTu_1clYOkNGrnBQf3ZQJJw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200813a180150.jpg&h=ffc0ddfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】一名駐守機動部隊的23歲男警員於本月9日已初步確診，但相隔5日直至今日才被列為確診個案，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君解釋，由於私人化驗所未有將樣本送到政府化驗所，需在衛生署主動追問下才收到，相信是送漏樣本造成延誤。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君形容個案是「比較例外」，相信私人化驗所不是故意。當被問到會否規定私人化驗所在指定限期內要將樣本送到衞生署、當樣本送遞延誤遲等情況是否需負上責任等，張竹君指希望他們將樣本盡快送遞，不是每件事都要有法律規限。"},{"pid":"9fec80dab3c8e9c273463853e9cdf941543e4d69","tid":2155222,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於私人化驗所未有將樣本送到政府化驗所，需在衛生署主動追問下才收到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢班人依家不斷製造自己無能既事出嚟<br />\n<br />\n去 JUSTIFY 中國人落嚟取代呢件事"},{"pid":"a43e85dc90ff14d16e347de05669e197c82eb204","tid":2155222,"uid":318339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c8fe23d5b4554efcfa54823903debf9998f8990","tid":2155222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Tu_1clYOkNGrnBQf3ZQJJw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200813a180150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTu_1clYOkNGrnBQf3ZQJJw--~A%2FYXBwa